	<div data-zesty-id="content:block:6-bcfbdaa6d3-vjj3qs:27:18:0:88">{{block('/-/block/hero_full.html?variant=7-eed0b8d1f7-n63g89')}}</div>
	<div class="p-6 rounded-5 bg-light mb-18" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:27:54">
<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:27:54-1:1 column - 1 row:0">
<div class="rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-dark-50 text-light" style="color:#FFFFFF;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:2:17"><h2 style="text-align:center;">1 in 5 Children in Oklahoma Go to Bed Hungry</h2>

<p style="text-align:center;">
	We provide programming to serve&nbsp;those who might not know where their next meal will come from.
</p></div>
<div class="py-5" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-xl:3:50"></div>
<h5 data-zesty-id="content:text:4:73">How we help Alleviate&nbsp;hunger</h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:5:40">In Oklahoma, Canadian, and Cleveland counties, we provide a food pantry open to the public. In Oklahoma and Cleveland counties we provide&nbsp;a nightly community meal.</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:6:80"><b>Community Meal</b></p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:7:29">
	In order help those in&nbsp;Central Oklahoma who face&nbsp;the daily burdens of food insecurity, we offer a free community meal every day.&nbsp;Anyone is welcome to come and share this meal.&nbsp;
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:8:13"><b>Client-Choice Food Pantry</b></p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:9:82">By supplying free fresh produce, canned goods, and healthy frozen items, our food pantries provide valuable meal supplementation while helping those in need maintain their independence and dignity. We provide the opportunity for clients to pick up food once every 30 days.</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:10:14">
	<span style="color:#ed1c2b;"><strong>Food drive donations are accepted at our offices.</strong></span>
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:11:55">
	<a href="https://www.usda.gov/non-discrimination-statement" target="">Usda Non-discrimination Statement</a>
</p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:12:42"></div>
<h6 data-zesty-id="content:text:14:5">For more information or to schedule an appointment contact:</h6>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:16:82"></div>
<div class="row g-3 my-3 align-items-stretch" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:19:12">
